2011-07-07T07:06:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/topro-technology-june-sales-fall-13-58-table-6236-tt.html
TOPRO TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 13.58% to NT$3,049,000 from NT$3,528,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             3,049            3,528     
YOY%             -13.58%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             18,189           24,410    
YOY%             -25.49% 
=================================================================
 